findings.remediation:
Add helmet middleware as the first middleware registered:

const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet());

This sets Content-Security-Policy, X-Frame-Options: SAMEORIGIN, X-Content-Type-Options: nosniff, Strict-Transport-Security, and removes X-Powered-By in a single call.
